  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Box-set tie-in novella for the Officio Assassinorum. Four operatives — a Vindicare sniper, an Eversor berserker, a Callidus shapeshifter and a Culexus pariah — are dispatched as a single Execution Force to stop Severin Drask, a Sorcerer-Lord of the Crimson Slaughter, before he completes a ritual at the Temple of Shades that would unleash a daemonic tide on the Imperium. The four temples are so doctrinally different that their cooperation is the central tension: Eversor psychosis grates against Culexus silence, Callidus shape-shifting collides with Vindicare discipline, and Crimson Slaughter cabalists hunt the team through the temple as the team hunts Drask. A heist-and-last-stand procedural at squad scale, structured around each temple's turn in the spotlight.",
